cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.DS 

The paper discusses the application of expectation propagation (EP) in machine learning, specifically in generalized linear models. This makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) the most likely sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of free probability theory, which falls under cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.SI (Systems and Control). The application of EP in approximate inference also relates to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the use of microarray datasets suggests a possible connection to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
